MLModelDescriptionKey: Detects the dominant objects present in an image from a set of 1001 categories such as trees, animals, food, vehicles, person etc. The top-1 accuracy from the original publication is 74.7%.
MLModelAuthorKey: Original Paper: Mark Sandler, Andrew Howard, Menglong Zhu, Andrey Zhmoginov, Liang-Chieh Chen.
MLModelLicenseKey: Please see https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow for license information, and https://github.com/tensorflow/models/tree/master/research/slim/nets/mobilenet for the original source of the model.
